    ["PRIESTSHADOWDUNGEONROTATION"] = "--OPENER-- \n\n[1] Precast Mind Blast\n[2] Cast Tentacle Slam\n[3] Cast Shadow Word: Pain\n[4] Cast Voidform\n[5] Cast Power Infusion + Use Tempered Potion + Any on use trinkets\n[6] Cast Void Volley\n[7] Cast Shadow Word: Madness\n[8] Cast Void Torrent\n[9] Cast Void Blast\n\n-ROTATION--\n\n[1] Cast Shadow Word: Pain to maintain Shadow Word: Pain\n[2] Maintain Vampiric Touch, either with Tentacle Slam or hard cast Vampiric Touch\n[3] Cast Voidform to enter Voidform\n[4] Cast Power Infusion\n[5] Cast Shadow Word: Death if the target has an absorb shield\n[6] Cast Void Blast if Shadow Word: Madness is active or if Entropic Rift is about to expire\n[7] Spend Insanity on Shadow Word: Madness if it is not active, is about to fall off, you are about to cap, or Entropic Rift is active\n[8] Cast Void Volley\n[9] Cast Void Torrent to activate Entropic Rift\n[10] Cast Mind Blast\n[11] Cast Shadow Word: Madness\n[12] Cast Tentacle Slam if there will be no additional targets to DoT or upcoming movement\n[13] Cast Mind Flay, interrupting as soon as anything of higher priority becomes available\n[14] When moving, cast Tentacle Slam, Shadow Word: Death, or Shadow Word: Pain to generate some Insanity and deal some damage",
