    ["DEATHKNIGHTUNHOLYDUNGEONROTATION"] = "--OPENER-- \n\n1. Cast Outbreak.\n\n2. Cast Festering Strike.\n\n3. Cast Festering Scythe.\n\n4. Cast Army of the Dead.\n\n5. Cast Dark Transformation.\n\n6. Use On-Use Trinket.\n\n7. Use Combat Potion.\n\n8. Cast Soul Reaper.\n\n9. Cast Necrotic Coil.\n\n10. Cast Necrotic Coil.\n\n-ROTATION--\n\nPriority outside of Forbidden Knowledge:\n\n1. Cast Outbreak if Virulent Plague is not active.\n\n2. Cast Army of the Dead on cooldown.\n\n3. Cast Dark Transformation on cooldown.\n\n4. Cast Putrefy If you have 2 charges.\n\n5. Cast Soul Reaper on cooldown.\n\n6. Cast Putrefy if Dark Transformation has 15 seconds or more left on its cooldown.\n\n7. Cast Festering Scythe if any target doesn't have its debuff, or its debuff is about to expire.\n\n8. Cast Death Coil if you have a Sudden Doom proc or 80 or more Runic Power.\n\n9. Cast Festering Strike if you have no Lesser Ghoul stacks.\n\n10. Cast Scourge Strike if you have Lesser Ghoul stacks.\n\n11. Cast Death Coil.\n\n\nPriority during Forbidden Knowledge:\n\n12. Cast Putrefy If you have 2 charges.\n\n13. Cast Soul Reaper on cooldown.\n\n14. Cast Festering Scythe if any target doesn't have its debuff, or its debuff is about to expire.\n\n15. Cast Necrotic Coil.\n\n16. Cast Festering Strike if you have no Lesser Ghoul stacks.\n\n17. Cast Scourge Strike if you have Lesser Ghoul stacks.",
