    ["DEATHKNIGHTFROSTDUNGEONROTATION"] = "--OPENER-- \n\n1. Empower Rune Weapon\n\n2. Reaper's Mark\n\n3. Pillar of Frost\n\n4. Breath of Sindragosa\n\n5. Obliterate\n\n6. Empower Rune Weapon\n\n7. Obliterate\n\n8. Continue with normal rotation.\n\n-ROTATION--\n\n1. Empower Rune Weapon if you have 2 charges\n\n2. Reaper's Mark\n\n3. Pillar of Frost\n\n4. Breath of Sindragosa\n\n5. Frostwyrm's Fury if you do not have an active Reaper's Mark or Exterminate\n\n6. Frostscythe if you have 2 Killing Machine stacks, or Exterminate\n\n7. Howling Blast with Rime\n\n8. Glacial Advance to avoid Runic Power waste\n\n9. Frostscythe with Killing Machine\n\n10. Empower Rune Weapon to generate Killing Machine\n\n11. Glacial Advance\n\n12. Frostscythe without Killing Machine\n\n13. Howling Blast",
    ["DEATHKNIGHTFROSTDELVEROTATION"] = "--OPENER-- \n\n1. Empower Rune Weapon\n\n2. Reaper's Mark\n\n3. Pillar of Frost\n\n4. Breath of Sindragosa\n\n5. Obliterate\n\n6. Empower Rune Weapon\n\n7. Obliterate\n\n8. Continue with normal rotation.\n\n-ROTATION--\n\n1. Empower Rune Weapon if you have 2 charges\n\n2. Reaper's Mark\n\n3. Pillar of Frost\n\n4. Breath of Sindragosa\n\n5. Frostwyrm's Fury if you do not have an active Reaper's Mark or Exterminate\n\n6. Frostscythe if you have 2 Killing Machine stacks, or Exterminate\n\n7. Howling Blast with Rime\n\n8. Glacial Advance to avoid Runic Power waste\n\n9. Frostscythe with Killing Machine\n\n10. Empower Rune Weapon to generate Killing Machine\n\n11. Glacial Advance\n\n12. Frostscythe without Killing Machine\n\n13. Howling Blast",
    ["DEATHKNIGHTFROSTRAIDAOEROTATION"] = "--OPENER-- \n\n1. Empower Rune Weapon\n\n2. Reaper's Mark\n\n3. Pillar of Frost\n\n4. Breath of Sindragosa\n\n5. Obliterate\n\n6. Empower Rune Weapon\n\n7. Obliterate\n\n8. Continue with normal rotation.\n\n-ROTATION--\n\n1. Empower Rune Weapon if you have 2 charges\n\n2. Reaper's Mark\n\n3. Pillar of Frost\n\n4. Breath of Sindragosa\n\n5. Frostwyrm's Fury if you do not have an active Reaper's Mark or Exterminate\n\n6. Frostscythe if you have 2 Killing Machine stacks, or Exterminate\n\n7. Howling Blast with Rime\n\n8. Glacial Advance to avoid Runic Power waste\n\n9. Frostscythe with Killing Machine\n\n10. Empower Rune Weapon to generate Killing Machine\n\n11. Glacial Advance\n\n12. Frostscythe without Killing Machine\n\n13. Howling Blast",
    ["DEATHKNIGHTFROSTRAIDSTROTATION"] = "--OPENER-- \n\n1. Empower Rune Weapon\n\n2. Reaper's Mark\n\n3. Pillar of Frost\n\n4. Breath of Sindragosa\n\n5. Obliterate\n\n6. Empower Rune Weapon\n\n7. Obliterate\n\n8. Continue with normal rotation.\n\n-ROTATION--\n\n1. Empower Rune Weapon if you have 2 charges\n\n2. Reaper's Mark\n\n3. Pillar of Frost\n\n4. Breath of Sindragosa\n\n5. Frostwyrm's Fury if you do not have an active Reaper's Mark or Exterminate\n\n6. Obliterate if you have 2 Killing Machine stacks, or Exterminate\n\n7. Howling Blast with Rime\n\n8. Frost Strike to avoid Runic Power waste\n\n9. Obliterate with Killing Machine\n\n10. Empower Rune Weapon to generate Killing Machine\n\n11. Frost Strike\n\n12. Obliterate without Killing Machine\n\n13. Howling Blast",
    ["DEATHKNIGHTBLOODRAIDROTATION"] = "--OPENER-- \n\n1. Cast Death's Caress\n\n2. While Death's Caress is in flight, pre-place Death and Decay\n\n3. Cast Dancing Rune Weapon\n\n4. Cast Blood Boil\n\n5. Cast Vampiric Strike\n\n6. Cast Vampiric Strike\n\n7. Cast Death Strike\n\n8. Proceed with normal priority\n\n-ROTATION--\n\nIn Gift of the San'layn:\n\n1. Cast Death Strike if you need the healing or are above 75 Runic Power.\n\n2. Maintain at least 5 charges of Bone Shield.\n\n3. Cast Blood Boil if the Blood Plague copy from Dancing Rune Weapon is not currently on your target.\n\n4. Cast Death and Decay if you have a Crimson Scourge proc.\n\n5. Fill with Vampiric Strike.\n\n6. If you run out of runes, cast Blood Boil.\n\n\nOutside Dancing Rune Weapon:\n\n7. Cast Death Strike if you need the healing or are above 75 Runic Power.\n\n8. Maintain at least 5 charges of Bone Shield. If Bone Shield is about to expire, press Marrowrend.\n\n9. Cast Death and Decay and stand in it if you are not currently affected by the buff it provides, or if you get a Crimson Scourge proc.\n\n10. Cast Blood Boil if you have a Boiling Point proc.\n\n11. Cast Vampiric Strike if it is available.\n\n12. Cast Blood Boil to prevent its charges from capping.\n\n13. Cast Heart Strike.",
    ["DEATHKNIGHTBLOODDELVEROTATION"] = "--OPENER-- \n\n1. Cast Death's Caress\n\n2. While Death's Caress is in flight, pre-place Death and Decay\n\n3. Cast Dancing Rune Weapon\n\n4. Cast Blood Boil\n\n5. Cast Vampiric Strike\n\n6. Cast Vampiric Strike\n\n7. Cast Death Strike\n\n8. Proceed with normal priority\n\n-ROTATION--\n\nIn Gift of the San'layn:\n\n1. Cast Death Strike if you need the healing or are above 75 Runic Power.\n\n2. Maintain at least 5 charges of Bone Shield.\n\n3. Cast Blood Boil if the Blood Plague copy from Dancing Rune Weapon is not currently on your target.\n\n4. Cast Death and Decay if you have a Crimson Scourge proc.\n\n5. Fill with Vampiric Strike.\n\n6. If you run out of runes, cast Blood Boil.\n\n\nOutside Dancing Rune Weapon:\n\n7. Cast Death Strike if you need the healing or are above 75 Runic Power.\n\n8. Maintain at least 5 charges of Bone Shield. If Bone Shield is about to expire, press Marrowrend.\n\n9. Cast Death and Decay and stand in it if you are not currently affected by the buff it provides, or if you get a Crimson Scourge proc.\n\n10. Cast Blood Boil if you have a Boiling Point proc.\n\n11. Cast Vampiric Strike if it is available.\n\n12. Cast Blood Boil to prevent its charges from capping.\n\n13. Cast Heart Strike.",
