    ["DEMONHUNTERHAVOCRAIDAOEROTATION"] = "--OPENER-- \n1. Cast Immolation Aura 1 GCD Pre-Pull\n\n2. Use Fleeting Tempered Potion and any on-use trinkets such as Araz's Ritual Forge.\n\n3. Cast The Hunt\n\n4. Cast Felblade\n\n5. Cast Eye Beam\n\n6. Cast Essence Break\n\n7. Cast Death Sweep\n\n8. Cast Death Sweep\n\n9. Cast Annihilation\n\n10. Cast Vengeful Retreat and Metamorphosis\n\n11. Cast Death Sweep\n\n12. Cast Fel Rush\n\n13. Cast Annihilation\n\n14. Cast Consuming Fire\n\n15. Cast Abyssal Gaze\n\n16. Continue with normal priority\n\n-ROTATION--\n\n1. If Inertia buff is up, Cast Felblade or Fel Rush to proc.\n\n2. Cast The Hunt.\n\n3. Cast Death Sweep.\n\n4. Cast Immolation Aura If capped on charges.\n\n5. Cast Vengeful Retreat if Eye Beam is off cooldown.\n\n6. Cast Eye Beam.\n\n7. Cast Essence Break while in Metamorphosis.\n\n8. Cast Metamorphosis.\n\n9. Cast Blade Dance.\n\n10. Cast Annihilation.\n\n11. Cast Chaos Strike.\n\n12. Cast Immolation Aura.\n\n13. Cast Felblade.\n\n14. Cast Throw Glaive or Fel Rush when no other abilities are available.",
    ["DEMONHUNTERHAVOCDUNGEONROTATION"] = "--OPENER-- \n1. Cast Immolation Aura 1 GCD Pre-Pull\n\n2. Use Fleeting Tempered Potion and any on-use trinkets such as Araz's Ritual Forge.\n\n3. Cast The Hunt\n\n4. Cast Felblade\n\n5. Cast Eye Beam\n\n6. Cast Essence Break\n\n7. Cast Death Sweep\n\n8. Cast Death Sweep\n\n9. Cast Annihilation\n\n10. Cast Vengeful Retreat and Metamorphosis\n\n11. Cast Death Sweep\n\n12. Cast Fel Rush\n\n13. Cast Annihilation\n\n14. Cast Consuming Fire\n\n15. Cast Abyssal Gaze\n\n16. Continue with normal priority\n\n-ROTATION--\n\n1. If Inertia buff is up, Cast Felblade or Fel Rush to proc.\n\n2. Cast The Hunt.\n\n3. Cast Death Sweep.\n\n4. Cast Immolation Aura If capped on charges.\n\n5. Cast Vengeful Retreat if Eye Beam is off cooldown.\n\n6. Cast Eye Beam.\n\n7. Cast Essence Break while in Metamorphosis.\n\n8. Cast Metamorphosis.\n\n9. Cast Blade Dance.\n\n10. Cast Annihilation.\n\n11. Cast Chaos Strike.\n\n12. Cast Immolation Aura.\n\n13. Cast Felblade.\n\n14. Cast Throw Glaive or Fel Rush when no other abilities are available.",
