    ["MAGEFIRERAIDSTROTATION"] = "--OPENER-- \nOPENER (FIRESTARTER)\n\n[1] Pre-cast Pyroblast before the pull (hard-cast).\n[2] Fireball.\n[3] Fire Blast during the Fireball cast.\n[4] Pyroblast with Hot Streak! twice\n[5] Alternate between Fire Blast and Pyroblast until you run out of charges.\n[6] If the target is still above 90% health, repeat the following:\n[1] Fireball\n[2] Fire Blast during the Fireball cast.\n[3] Without Hot Streak!, Fireball again.\n[4] Pyroblast with Hot Streak! twice\n\nENTERING COMBUSTION\n\n[1] Pyroblast to spend your Hot Streak!.\n[2] AoE Only: Precast Meteor, before your Scorch cast.\n[3] Begin a Scorch cast.\n[4] Fire Blast as soon as the Scorch cast begins.\n[5] Combustion right before the Scorch cast ends.\n[6] Pyroblast (or Flamestrike in AoE) with Hot Streak! twice\n\n-ROTATION--\n\nDuring Combustion, all of your casts will Critically strike. This means that you will alternate between Pyroblast (with Hot Streak!) and builders.\n\n[1] Meteor in the last 8 seconds of Combustion.\n[2] Pyroblast with Hot Streak!\n[3] Pyroblast again if you just spent Hot Streak! at the end of a Scorch cast.\n\nThe below casts are used to generate Hot Streak!:\n\nFire Blast.\n\nScorch as filler.\n\nPriority (Outside Combustion)\n\n[1] Cast Combustion.\n[2] Pyroblast with Hot Streak!.\n[3] Pyroblast with Hyperthermia.\n[4] Cast Fire Blast if you have Heating Up while casting Fireball.\n[5] Cast Fire Blast if you just spent Hot Streak! and are guaranteed to Crit: Pyroblast is in flight during Hyperthermia.\n[6] In Execute: Cast Fire Blast without Heating Up while casting Scorch.\n[7] In Execute: If you have Heating Up.\n[8] Scorch with Heat Shimmer after spending Hot Streak!.\n[9] In Execute: Scorch if the target is below 30% health.\n[10] Fireball as filler.",
    ["MAGEFROSTDUNGEONROTATION"] = "--OPENER-- \n\n[1] Glacial Spike\n[2] Flurry\n[3] Frozen Orb\n[4] Ray of Frost\n\n-ROTATION--\n\n[1] Blizzard if Freezing Rain is active\n[2] Flurry if Brain Freeze is active and Thermal Void is not active\n[3] Ice Lance if Fingers of Frost at 2 stacks\n[4] Frozen Orb\n[5] Glacial Spike\n[6] Ice Lance if Fingers of Frost is active\n[7] Ice Lance if Freezing at 6 or more stacks\n[8] Flurry\n[9] Ray of Frost\n[10] Frostbolt",
    ["MAGEFROSTDELVEROTATION"] = "--OPENER-- \n\n[1] Glacial Spike\n[2] Flurry\n[3] Frozen Orb\n[4] Ray of Frost\n\n-ROTATION--\n\n[1] Blizzard if Freezing Rain is active\n[2] Flurry if Brain Freeze is active and Thermal Void is not active\n[3] Ice Lance if Fingers of Frost at 2 stacks\n[4] Frozen Orb\n[5] Glacial Spike\n[6] Ice Lance if Fingers of Frost is active\n[7] Ice Lance if Freezing at 6 or more stacks\n[8] Flurry\n[9] Ray of Frost\n[10] Frostbolt",
