    ["MAGEFROSTRAIDSTROTATION"] = "--OPENER-- \n\n[1] Glacial Spike\n[2] Flurry\n[3] Frozen Orb\n[4] Ray of Frost\n\n-ROTATION--\n\n[1] Flurry if Brain Freeze is active and Thermal Void is not active\n[2] Ice Lance if Fingers of Frost at 2 stacks\n[3] Frozen Orb\n[4] Glacial Spike\n[5] Ice Lance if Fingers of Frost is active\n[6] Ice Lance if Freezing at 6 or more stacks\n[7] Flurry\n[8] Ray of Frost\n[9] Frostbolt",
    ["MONKBREWMASTERDUNGEONROTATION"] = "--OPENER-- \n\n[1] Use Chi Burst from a distance, and move toward your target\n[2] Use Keg Smash while moving to your target\n[3] Use Blackout Kick\n[4] Use Breath of Fire\n[5] Use Tiger Palm\n[6] Use Exploding Keg\n[7] Use Keg Smash\n[8] Use Blackout Kick\n[9] Activate Invoke Niuzao, the Black Ox\n[10] From here, follow the rotational priorities below\n\n-ROTATION--\n\n[1] Execute an enemy with Touch of Death, when allowed\n[2] Use Blackout Kick to trigger Blackout Combo\n[3] Cast Chi Burst\n[4] Consume one charge of Celestial Brew / Celestial Infusion, only if at two charges or taking minimal damage\n[5] Activate Invoke Niuzao, the Black Ox\n[6] Consume your Blackout Combo buff with Tiger Palm\n[7] Use Breath of Fire\n[8] Use your first charge of Keg Smash or an active Empty Barrel from Bring Me Another\n[9] Use Exploding Keg\n[10] Use your second charge of Keg Smash\n[11] If taking minimal damage, use an extra charge of Purifying Brew to trigger additional Special Delivery or Empty Barrels from Bring Me Another\n[12] Use Tiger Palm when there are no other abilities to press",
