    ["MONKMISTWEAVERDELVEROTATION"] = "[1] Sheilun's Gift to keep someone alive that would otherwise die without your intervention\n[2] Debuff enemies with Mystic Touch\n[3] Revival or Sheilun's Gift\n[4] Heart of the Jade Serpent abilities while under its effects Priority\n[5] Renewing Mist if at 3 charges\n[6] Mana Tea if at 20 Mana Tea stacks\n[7] Rising Sun Kick\n[8] Invoke Chi-Ji, the Red Crane or Celestial Conduit\n[9] Enveloping Mist if at 2 Spiritfont stacks\n[10] Thunder Focus Tea\n[11] Renewing Mist\n[12] Enveloping Mist with Strength of the Black Ox\n[13] Blackout Kick\n[14] Tiger Palm\n[15] Mana Tea",
    ["MONKMISTWEAVERRAIDROTATION"] = "[1] Vivify to keep someone alive that would otherwise die without your intervention\n[2] Debuff enemies with Mystic Touch\n[3] Restoral when it is assigned\n[4] Heart of the Jade Serpent abilities while under its effects Priority\n[5] Renewing Mist if at 3 charges\n[6] Mana Tea if at 20 Mana Tea stacks\n[7] Rushing Wind Kick\n[8] Invoke Yu'lon, the Jade Serpent or Celestial Conduit, when it is assigned\n[9] Vivify if at 2 Zen Pulse stacks\n[10] Enveloping Mist if at 2 Spiritfont stacks\n[11] Thunder Focus Tea\n[12] Renewing Mist\n[13] Vivify\n[14] Enveloping Mist with Strength of the Black Ox\n[15] Mana Tea\n[16] Blackout Kick to fill\n[17] Tiger Palm to fill",
    ["MONKWINDWALKERDUNGEONROTATION"] = "--OPENER-- \n\n[1] Cast Tiger Palm\n[2] Cast Zenith with potions, racials, and trinkets. Stat buffs go before Zenith.\n[3] Cast Fists of Fury\n[4] Cast Rising Sun Kick\n[5] Cast Fists of Fury if Rising Sun Kick reset your Fists of Fury cooldown.\n[6] Cast Whirling Dragon Punch\n[7] Proceed with normal priority\n\n\n-ROTATION--\n\n[1] Cast Touch of Death\n[2] Cast Whirling Dragon Punch\n[3] Cast Tiger Palm if less than 4 Chi, less than 2 stacks of Combo Breaker, AND about to cap energy\n[4] Cast Fists of Fury\n[5] Cast Rushing Wind Kick\n[6] Cast Spinning Crane Kick with less than 4 seconds remaining on Dance of Chi-Ji AND not at 2 stacks of Combo Breaker\n[7] Cast Rising Sun Kick\n[8] Cast Tiger Palm if not enough Chi for the above\n[9] Cast Blackout Kick with Combo Breaker or Zenith active\n[10] Cast Spinning Crane Kick with Zenith active AND more than 3 Chi\n[11] Cast Spinning Crane Kick with Dance of Chi-Ji\n[12] Cast Blackout Kick\n[13] Cast Spinning Crane Kick\n[14] Cast Tiger Palm",
